Proof of concept to get Wifi keys from Telefonica provider.

Simple script to test de weak security of Telefonica WEP keys.
Basically it does:
 - Run kismet to capture wifi packages
 - Run wlandecrypter to generate candidate keys
 - Run weplab to test the keys

------------------------------
INSTALL:
Prerequisites
 $ sudo apt-get installÂ  perl xterm kismet weplab
 $ wget http://wlandecrypter.googlecode.com/files/wlandecrypter-1.2.tar.gz
 $ tar xzf wlandecrypter-1.2.tar.gz
 $ cd wlandecrypter-1.2
 $ make
 $ sudo make install
Installation
 $ wget http://github.com/DavidEGx/wlanXcript/tarball/master
 $ tar xzf wlanXcrypt
 $ cd wlanXcrypt
 $ chmod +x wlanXcrypt


USAGE:
 $ sudo perl ./wlanXcript.pl

